Package: isnanReprex
Type: Package
Title: Reprex for TMB/Rcpp Macro Definition Order Conflicts
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: person("Sam", "Johnson",
    email = "sdnjohnson@landmarkfisheries.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Demonstrates macro conflicts when TMB.hpp and
    Rcpp.h are included in the same translation unit. TMB
    re-exports R macros (ISNAN, isNull, length) that collide
    with Rcpp class methods and template code. The only
    working include order is Rcpp before TMB.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
Imports: TMB, RcppEigen, Rcpp
LinkingTo: TMB, RcppEigen, Rcpp
